Business Recommendations:

- Scale revenue in the Americas (especially the US) by optimizing logistics for high order volumes, while testing premium segments to lift AOV.
- Grow Europe's revenue by increasing order volume, leveraging its already high conversion rate.
- Maintain a balanced product mix: mass-market categories (bookcases, chairs) for customer acquisition and volume, premium categories (sofas, beds) for margin via upselling/cross-selling.
- Prioritize desktop and Organic Search as core revenue channels; invest in mobile to capture growth in mass-market purchases.
- Focus retention efforts on subscribed users (5x higher revenue) by reducing unsubscribe rates through personalized, segmented email campaigns.
- Concentrate seasonal marketing budget (Paid Search) around the November-December peak, when revenue is most sensitive to promotions.
